1
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,120
When are you leaving?

2
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,360
Today.

3
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,400
Don't worry.

4
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,370
The matter is handled well.

5
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,080
You are running away.

6
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,740
And you say it's handled well?

7
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,960
Mind your own business.

8
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,960
I can just change my identity again.

9
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:07,120
This setup was too risky.

10
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,360
You should have been more careful.

11
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:14,440
Could it be riskier than what you did a year ago?

12
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,360
Am I wrong,

13
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,320
Emily?

14
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:30,360
We are being targeted by the police now,

15
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,880
and it's all thanks to you.

16
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:34,320
Don't forget,

17
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,079
your good sister,

18
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,520
Officer Zhuang Lan.

19
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:41,079
She's always been looking for Lighthouse.

20
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,560
It's getting late.

21
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,490
I'm leaving now.

22
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,079
Good luck.

23
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:52,920
Bye.

24
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:56,160
Good luck to you too.

25
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,320
Fang,

26
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,840
set up checkpoints at the bus station and the docks immediately.

27
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,920
She'll probably want to leave Mancheng as soon as possible.

28
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,320
We can't let her succeed.

29
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,320
Bai,

30
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,960
go visit her neighbors again,

31
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,000
as well as her colleagues.

32
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:19,600
She's very likely hiding in one of their homes.

33
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:21,120
We can't miss anything.

34
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,850
Understood.

35
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,720
Shao.

36
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:25,000
Go to her house for another trace identification,

37
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,000
to see if there are any new discoveries.

38
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,680
Understood.

39
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,440
Let's go.

40
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:42,370
It wasn't me.

41
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:44,640
Xiaobai asked me to give it to you.

42
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:46,960
Thank you.

43
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,040
Tell me,

44
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:56,320
when exactly did we leak the information

45
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,100
that let her escape early?

46
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,760
Remember I told you,

47
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,600
walls have ears in this world.

48
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,680
Fortunately,

49
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:08,600
the chief has agreed to issue an investigation notice for her.

50
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:10,840
She will be wanted across the city soon.

51
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,850
She won't escape this time.

52
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,440
I won't allow myself to fail again.

53
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,399
You won't.

54
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,440
Drink your coffee first.

55
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:33,960
Move.

56
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,520
What's in this bag?

57
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,920
Open it.

58
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,080
ID card.

59
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,400
Okay, next.

60
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,600
Anyway,

61
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,460
at least we have a definite target this time.

62
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,240
That is still some progress.

63
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,140
It's getting late.

64
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,890
Everyone, go back and rest.

65
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:28,680
Sis.

66
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,300
Let Captain Zhuang get some rest.

67
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,520
Sis,

68
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,320
we'll be leaving now.

69
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,520
Let's go.

70
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,050
Let's go.

71
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,060
Captain Zhuang, we'll head back now.

72
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,960
Accident.

73
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:26,080
It's the lighthouse's design.

74
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,840
There's no time.

75
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:31,000
They found me.

76
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,320
I can't leave.

77
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,640
Accidents or tomorrow,

78
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,440
which will come first?

79
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,440
Hello? Where are you?

80
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:55,840
I can't leave.

81
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,040
The train station is full of cops.

82
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,600
Arrange for me to leave now.

83
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,280
Right now, hurry!

84
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,960
Then wait for me at the cafe entrance now.

85
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:04,880
Okay.

86
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,080
In such a hurry to leave?

87
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,810
Let me see you off one last time.

88
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,480
Didn't you get off work?

89
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,409
Why are you back?

90
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,360
Sister.

91
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,960
As your subordinate,

92
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,820
I get off work when my boss says so.

93
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,760
But you are unhappy.

94
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,640
As your good sister,

95
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,640
I definitely have to accompany you.

96
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,480
Fine, you're sweet.

97
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,560
You, Shao.

98
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,080
What about you?

99
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,480
Finally got a clue.

100
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,160
After tonight,

101
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,720
there will be more variables tomorrow.

102
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,280
Besides,

103
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,380
I don't believe I can't catch her.

104
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,380
That's your style.

105
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:18,170
The young man is really energetic.

106
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,400
This comrade,

107
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:24,600
usually runs faster than anyone after work.

108
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,460
Why aren't you leaving this time?

109
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,400
Well,

110
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,800
if there's nothing to do,

111
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,040
who doesn't want to get off work early?

112
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,200
But I've never slacked off when there's work.

113
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,730
After all, I'm getting old.

114
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:35,919
I need less sleep.

115
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,340
What about you?

116
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:47,850
I'm waiting for you to take me home.

117
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,160
Mr. Cheng.

118
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:51,920
Amazing.

119
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:52,580
Brilliant.

120
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,600
Alright.

121
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,160
Since everyone wants to stay,

122
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:01,240
it seems we'll be working overtime tonight.

123
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,920
I'll treat you to late-night snacks.

124
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,000
I'll go.

125
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,240
You actually know how to treat people?

126
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,080
I can.

127
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,720
This kid runs so fast.

128
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:15,010
Almost as fast as I did when I was young.

129
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,160
Hello?

130
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:22,840
It's me.

131
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,040
Is everything all right?

132
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,520
You found Liu Ying?

133
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:29,800
That's great.

134
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:30,840
Where is she?

135
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,400
What?

136
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,280
Dead?

137
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,600
Mr. Shao,

138
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,400
you head to the scene first.

139
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,600
We'll be right there.

140
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,800
Notify Mia and Awang.

141
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:40,400
Okay.

142
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,380
Where is Mr. Cheng?

143
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:46,760
Oh right.

144
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:47,760
Forgot about him.

145
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:49,920
Forget it, let's not wait.

146
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:50,520
Let's go.

147
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,080
Go.

148
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:55,840
Shao.

149
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,640
Liu Ying.

150
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,440
Shao.

151
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:02,970
How is it?

152
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,760
The massive impact caused multiple fractures all over her body,

153
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,840
and she died from severe internal bleeding.

154
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,200
This is clearly murder.

155
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,720
We were just about to investigate her,

156
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,560
and she dies.

157
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,840
It means we're looking in the right direction.

158
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,570
We're right.

159
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:20,360
It means we hit a sore spot,

160
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,600
the core of the Lighthouse organization.

161
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:24,960
Right.

162
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,320
These people are acting out of desperation.

163
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,720
They even kill their own.

164
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:39,680
This is the only surveillance video from the scene.

165
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:41,320
After processing by the technical department,

166
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,320
it's already the clearest version.

167
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,000
We still can't see who it is.

168
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,120
Sis,

169
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:50,380
aren't you afraid you won't see me again?

170
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,920
I promise you.

171
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:54,200
I'll visit you when I have time, okay?

172
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,600
Xiaobai.

173
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,720
Go and check

174
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,780
the owner's information of this car.

175
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,840
Bring her to me.

176
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,180
Got it, Sister.

177
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:09,920
I'll go to the scene

178
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,880
to check all the surveillance footage around it

179
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,480
and see if we can

180
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,080
find the direction she fled.

181
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,360
Is this you?

182
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,200
Zhuang Qing.

183
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:25,080
Could I have made a mistake?

184
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,800
Shao just said Liu Ying died.

185
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,460
We were a step too late.

186
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,680
Your micro-expressions tell me

187
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,680
you've guessed the killer's identity.

188
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,340
Others couldn't tell who she was.

189
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,540
But I recognized immediately

190
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,600
that she was my sister.

191
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,760
But she was already dead.

192
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,690
I saw her die in front of me with my own eyes.

193
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,480
I have a question.

194
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,410
Is she your biological sister?

195
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:22,280
My father brought her back.

196
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,680
She is not my biological sister.

197
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:27,240
But we grew up together.

198
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:30,060
I always treated her like my biological sister.

199
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,400
I knew it.

200
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,960
If a dead person suddenly comes back,

201
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:39,010
there is only one possibility.

202
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:41,140
She is not the same person.

203
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,720
I know that place.

204
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:53,850
I'll take you there.

205
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:04,180
This is the last place Zhuang Qing visited before she died.

206
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,640
Accidents and tomorrow

207
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,800
will arrive at the same time.

208
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:29,200
It really is her.

209
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,600
Solving these tricks

210
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,600
and finding the truth behind the accidents

211
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:50,000
is the purpose of our department.

212
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:55,280
Ahead,

213
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:58,580
there are more difficulties waiting for us.

214
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,960
Accident Investigation Team, attention!

215
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,840
Here!

216
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,240
Move out.

217
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,240
Copy that.
